mcqs.question:
Consider the following code:

#pragma omp parallel
#pragma omp single
{
 #pragma omp task
 { process_data(10); }
 printf("Task created\n");
}

What is the correct order of execution?

Consider this code with task dependencies:

#pragma omp parallel
#pragma omp single
{
 #pragma omp task depend(in: a) depend(out: b)
 { process1(); }
 #pragma omp task depend(in: b) depend(out: c)
 { process2(); }
}

Which statement is correct about execution order?
